#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>: Edit tags."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>T</keycap></"
