"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Del</keycap></"
"keycombo>: briše sliku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo>: Copy an "
